data.description: Charming 1-story, 3 bed/ 2 bath with 1656 sq ft of living space. Located in the beautiful neighborhood of Valley Ranch! The open floor plan features high ceilings, spacious rooms and open kitchen. The kitchen features an island, stainless steel appliances, and gas stove. Master bedroom has a walk-in closet and a full bath with a shower. This DR Horton home is located in a great neighborhood with schools in close proximity. The 1-story family home was built in 2019 by one of the top name builders in Texas! Come see this wonderful house today, and experience all that this home has to offer. ***Seller to contribute $5,000 in seller concessions with listed price offer***
